{
    "conversation": {
        "startCondition": {
            "participant": {
                "name": "default",
                "line": {
                    "text": "%PLAYER%: You're the last of their leaders! Your army has no choice but to turn back and leave Avalon alone.",
                    "response": {
                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                        "line": {
                            "soundtoplay": "voice/petrovitch/2_jungle2_020_011",
                            "text": "%Petrovitch%: Nyet! This is impossible! Mikhail assured me you would never get this far!",
                            "response": {
                                "tagjump": "autogen_tag_1",
                                "text": "%BLANK%"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "startCondition": {
            "participant": {
                "name": "default",
                "line": {
                    "soundtoplay": "voice/petrovitch/2_jungle2_020_020",
                    "text": "%Petrovitch%: Go away! I have told you everything I know.",
                    "response": {
                        "tagjump": "autogen_tag_1",
                        "text": "%BLANK%"
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "startCondition": {
            "participant": {
                "name": "default",
                "line": {
                    "tagindex": "autogen_tag_1",
                    "text": "%PLAYER%",
                    "response": {
                        "text": "Who's Mikhail?",
                        "line": {
                            "soundtoplay": "voice/petrovitch/2_jungle2_020_031",
                            "text": "%Petrovitch%: Mikhail Rasputin is our leader. You would do well to fear him for he is a Horseman of Apocalypse.",
                            "response": {
                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "text": "%PLAYER%: But he's Colossus' older brother.",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/petrovitch/2_jungle2_020_033",
                                            "text": "%Petrovitch%: Da. And he will be enraged when he hears you were the reason for our failure. If you value your lives you will flee now.",
                                            "response": {
                                                "tagjump": "autogen_tag_1",
                                                "text": "%BLANK%"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "response": {
                        "text": "Why were you going to attack Avalon?",
                        "line": {
                            "soundtoplay": "voice/petrovitch/2_jungle2_020_041",
                            "text": "%Petrovitch%: Mikhail knew you would be coming. He wanted to force you to leave the Savage Land so you would not disrupt his search for 'The Four'.",
                            "response": {
                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "text": "%PLAYER%: What do you mean 'The Four'?",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/petrovitch/2_jungle2_020_043",
                                            "text": "%Petrovitch%: All Mikhail told us was that Apocalypse is searching for four mutants with a particular DNA.",
                                            "response": {
                                                "tagjump": "autogen_tag_1",
                                                "text": "%BLANK%"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "response": {
                        "text": "Where can we find Beast?",
                        "line": {
                            "soundtoplay": "voice/petrovitch/2_jungle2_020_051",
                            "text": "%Petrovitch%: I will tell you nothing. Mikhail would kill me.",
                            "response": {
                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "text": "%PLAYER%: Okay, if that's how you want it. Professor Xavier? Would you rip Beast's location from this man's mind?",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/profx/2_jungle2_020_053",
                                            "text": "%ProfX%: Very well, but does he understand the process is extremely painful? And it could damage his long-term memory?",
                                            "response": {
                                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                                "line": {
                                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/petrovitch/2_jungle2_020_054",
                                                    "text": "%Petrovitch%: No, wait! Wait! I will tell you everything!",
                                                    "response": {
                                                        "tagjump": "autogen_tag_1",
                                                        "text": "%BLANK%"
                                                    }
                                                }
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "response": {
                        "text": "So talk. Where's Beast?",
                        "line": {
                            "soundtoplay": "voice/petrovitch/2_jungle2_020_061",
                            "text": "%Petrovitch%: He is being held prisoner in an ancient underground Nuwali temple. But it cannot be reached on foot and you cannot use your X-Jet. We have hidden surface to air rocket launchers everywhere.",
                            "response": {
                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "text": "%PLAYER%: Thanks. That's all we need to know. And thank you for your help, Professor Xavier.",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/profx/2_jungle2_020_063",
                                            "text": "%ProfX%: Anytime. And sir, I do hope you realize I was only bluffing. I would never have attempted to read your mind without your consent.",
                                            "response": {
                                                "tagjump": "autogen_tag_1",
                                                "text": "%BLANK%"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "response": {
                        "text": "Thanks. You were a lot of help.",
                        "line": {
                            "soundtoplay": "voice/petrovitch/2_jungle2_020_072",
                            "text": "%Petrovitch%: You will not be so smug when you meet Mikhail. He will destroy you.",
                            "response": {
                                "chosenscriptfile": "act2/jungle/jungle2/act2_obj_2_comp",
                                "conversationend": true,
                                "text": "%BLANK%"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}